OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry, bright morning,
OL,6,Fperhaps the odd light shower. Turning
OL,7,Fovercast through the afternoon as rain
OL,8,Farrives from the west, occasionally
OL,9,Fheavy. Blustery winds developing,
OL,10,Foccasionally strong in west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy, damp evening with
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy rain spreading
OL,14,Feastwards. Turning drier through the
OL,15,Frest of the night with some clearer
OL,16,Fspells developing. Blustery winds,
OL,17,Fstrong at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
