OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,6,Fdry day with some good sunny spells.
OL,7,FJust a low chance of the odd light
OL,8,Fshower.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,11,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,12,Ffew days with spells of rain, but a
OL,13,Fgood deal of dry and bright weather in
OL,14,Fthe east.
